title: ‘Mayor of Kingstown’ Season 1 Postmortem
description:
Cellmates Chris Ryan and Shea Serrano break down Season 1 of ‘Mayor of Kingstown’ (spoilers ahead!) and talk about their top five moments from the show that they can’t believe made it onto their televisions.
Hosts: Chris Ryan and Shea Serrano
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
